com.facebook.buck.apple

Class ProvisioningProfileMetadata.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.apple.ProvisioningProfileMetadata.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ProvisioningProfileMetadata

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ProvisioningProfileMetadata.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of ProvisioningProfileMetadata. Initialize attributes and then invoke build() method to create immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread safe and generally should not be stored in field or collection, but used immediately to create instances.
